OL,6,FReform UK's 'contract' of pledges was
OL,7,Funveiled on Monday and included a zero
OL,8,Ftolerance approach to policing which
OL,9,FToby Rhodes-Matthews says takes its
OL,10,Finfluence from the New York model and
OL,11,Fapproach.
OL,13,FHe said: "Look at the protests about
OL,14,FPalestine for example, the police are
OL,15,Fstanding back and not getting involved.
OL,17,F"Zero tolerance is the police going
OL,18,Fin, getting into the areas where they
OL,19,Fknow there's trouble, stop and
OL,20,Fsearching looking for knives to stop
OL,21,Fthat crime."
