OL,11,FChanging the 9-5 to a four-day week
OL,13,FThe Green Party's manifesto includes
OL,14,Fsome unique pledges including a four-
OL,15,Fday week, which the Wales leader
OL,16,Fbelieves will help with recruitment
OL,17,Fand retention of nurses and doctors.
