OL,6,FAnthony Slaughter said: "Where it's
OL,7,Fbeen trialled it's a great success.
OL,8,FIt's about quality of life. Years ago
OL,9,Fwe thought we'd be working a three-day
OL,10,Fweek by now. People need time to enjoy
OL,11,Flife and spend time with their
OL,12,Ffamilies.
OL,14,F"What you find with companies that
OL,15,Fhave trialled it is productivity goes
OL,16,Fup because people are happier and more
OL,17,Fcomfortable."
