OL,6,FBut the UK is struggling to recruit
OL,7,Fdoctors, nurses and teachers currently
OL,8,Fand more may be needed to cover
OL,9,Fshifts. "I'd argue a four day week
OL,10,Fmakes that kind of work more
OL,11,Fdesirable," Mr Slaughter said.
