OL,6,FBy reversing tax cuts given to banks,
OL,7,Fa 'windfall supertax' on oil and gas
OL,8,Fcompanies - plus by taxing frequent
OL,9,Fflyers, they say. "They've had a whale
OL,10,Fof a time over the last 14 years," Mr
OL,11,FChadwick said, "and it's about time we
OL,12,Frestored the tax burden to them and
OL,13,Fnot individuals."
OL,15,FReform UK claims it would lift 7.5
OL,16,Fmillion people out of paying tax by
OL,17,Fchanging the threshold at which people
OL,18,Fstart paying tax to #20,000, and
OL,19,Fpaying higher rate from #70,000.
