OL,6,FHow will they achieve this? "It's
OL,7,Fpublic services that we're going to
OL,8,Ftake our money from," Toby Rhodes-
OL,9,FMatthews said.
OL,11,F"We're going to be looking at
OL,12,Freforming the civil service - we're
OL,13,Fnot talking about making cuts to the
OL,14,Ffrontline - but what we're doing is
OL,15,Flooking to draw money, make savings,
OL,16,Fand push that back in to the frontline
OL,17,Ffor the people.
OL,19,F"It's those that are on the lower
OL,20,Fincomes that are going to feel the
OL,21,Fbenefit of this," he added.
