OL,6,FGreen Party candidate Anthony
OL,7,FSlaughter says he - and his party -
OL,8,Fare not afraid to talk about tax. They
OL,9,Fwant to raise #151bn in taxes by the
OL,10,Fend of the decade to tackle the crises
