OL,6,FFor the Liberal Democrats, it would be
OL,7,Fa Welsh revival. They would be
OL,8,Fdisappointed if, come July 5th, there
OL,9,Fwasn't a single Welsh Lib Dem MP.
OL,11,FThe Green Party know they are unlikely
OL,12,Fto win a seat, but the strategy is to
OL,13,Fgarner enough support to make a win at
OL,14,Fthe 2026 Senedd Election more likely.
OL,16,FReform UK also isn't expecting any
OL,17,FWelsh MPs but will keep an eye on
OL,18,Fwhere they come second, and who they
OL,19,Ftake votes from. It will be one of the
OL,20,Fbig themes come election night.
